        {
            "title": "港府1052億基建債 資金分配予20項目",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"港府1052億基建債 資金分配予20項目\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/H7ZlFLOK6iMIv9uCYRfjNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/398d43d0-d7bf-11f0-9fd3-22082a4478a5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">港府1052億基建債 資金分配予20項目</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
