        {
            "title": "華爾街日報：川普將沃什和哈塞特列為最有希望的聯儲會主席候選人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普表示，凱文·哈塞特和凱文·沃什是他首選的兩位聯儲會主席候選人，其希望下一任央行行長在利率問題上能與他進行磋商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周五在接受《華爾街日報》採訪時暗示沃什在候選人名單中的排名上升，而哈塞特此前被許多人視為該職位的領跑者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我覺得兩位凱文都很棒，」川普說。「我認為還有其他幾位也很出色。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Names Warsh, Hassett as Top Fed Chair Contenders, WSJ Says</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b041a21-cca2-35ef-87bb-aa291610fa0e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%87%E6%B2%83%E4%BB%80%E5%92%8C%E5%93%88%E5%A1%9E%E7%89%B9%E5%88%97%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%9A%84%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA-205902755.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-13 05:45:42",
